Package jdkc_exchange

Class SiteManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • jdkc_exchange.SiteManager
  • public class SiteManager
extends java.lang.Object
    A class which implements an aggregate of classes. The SiteManager class gathers together and organizes instances of the system and provides functionality for using and accessing instances in the aggregate.
    See Also:
    PersistenceManager
